=== 發展 ===
2007年2月，華納兄弟宣布，他們聘請了{{link-en|基蘭·馬爾羅尼|Kieran Mulroney}}和蜜雪兒夫妻兩人撰寫一份《正義聯盟》的劇本<ref>{{cite news | author = Pamela McClintock; Ben Fritz | title = 'Justice' prevails for Warner Bros. | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117960018 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2007-02-22 | accessdate = 2007-04-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110523152754/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117960018 | archive-date = 2011-05-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。後來，在差不多的時間傳出[[喬斯·溫登|喬斯·溫登]]長期計劃的《神力女超人》<ref>{{cite news|author=Jennifer Vineyard|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1551562/joss-whedon-wont-write-direct-wonder-woman-despite-doing-a-lot-of-legwork/|title=Joss Whedon Won’t Write, Direct ‘Wonder Woman’ — Despite Doing ‘A Lot Of Legwork’|publisher=MTV News|date=2007-02-02|accessdate=2014-09-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007184245/http://www.mtv.com/news/1551562/joss-whedon-wont-write-direct-wonder-woman-despite-doing-a-lot-of-legwork/|archivedate=2014-10-07}}</ref>和[[大衛·S·高耶|大衛·S·高耶]]編劇兼執導的《閃電俠》已取消<ref>{{cite news | author = Jessica Barnes | url = http://blog.moviefone.com/2007/02/03/david-goyer-booted-off-the-flash/ | title = David Goyer Booted Off The Flash | work = {{link-en|Moviefone|Moviefone}} | date = 2007-02-03 | accessdate = 2010-12-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110725173738/http://blog.moviefone.com/2007/02/03/david-goyer-booted-off-the-flash/ | archivedate = 2011-07-25 }}</ref>。據報導，該片的標題為《Justice League: Mortal》<ref name=tax>{{cite news | author = Michaela Boland | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117983131 | title = Will Australia get ''Justice League''? | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2008-03-28 | accessdate = 2008-11-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020072957/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117983131 | archivedate = 2012-10-20 }}</ref>；蜜雪兒和基蘭於2007年6月提交了劇本，獲得了華納兄弟積極的反應<ref>{{cite news | author = Pamela McClintock | title = ''Justice League'' film gets script | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117967042 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2007-06-15 | accessdate = 2008-03-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110128134134/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117967042 | archivedate = 2011-01-28 }}</ref>，因此華納兄弟希望能在[[2007年－2008年美國編劇協會大罷工|2007年－2008年美國編劇協會大罷工]]開始前拍攝<ref name="Diane Garrett">{{cite news | author = Diane Garrett | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117972369 | title = George Miller to lead ''Justice League'' | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2007-09-20 | accessdate = 2007-09-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120329050152/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117972369 | archivedate = 2012-03-29 }}</ref>。華納兄弟因為面對《[[超人再起|超人再起]]》失敗的票房與評價而不太願意繼續發展其續集。[[布蘭登·勞斯|布蘭登·勞斯]]並未被獲選為《Justice League: Mortal》中的超人一角<ref>{{cite news | author = Frosty | url = http://www.collider.com/entertainment/interviews/article.asp/aid/7675/tcid/1 | work = Collider.com | title = Brandon Routh Exclusive Video Interview – ''Lie To Me'' | date = 2008-04-23 | accessdate = 2008-11-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081021012959/http://www.collider.com/entertainment/interviews/article.asp/aid/7675/tcid/1 | archivedate = 2008-10-21 }}</ref>，且也不是《[[蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻]]》的[[克里斯汀·貝爾|克里斯汀·貝爾]]<ref name="Bale interview justice">{{cite news | author = Rachel Howard | title = Interview: Is Christian Bale In or Out of WB’s 'Justice League'? | url = http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3109&Itemid=99 | work = IESB | date = 2007-08-21 | accessdate = 2008-11-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080315113105/http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3109&Itemid=99 | archivedate = 2008-03-15 }}</ref>。華納兄弟擬定《Justice League: Mortal》是一個全新開始的系列，並發展到多部續集和番外篇<ref name=NYT/>。[[傑森·瑞特曼|傑森·瑞特曼]]曾是電影的導演人選，但他因想作為一名獨立電影的工作者而拒絕了這份工作<ref>{{cite news | author = Peter Sciretta | title = Jason Reitman Turns Down ''Justice League'' | url = http://www.slashfilm.com/2008/04/10/jason-reitman-turns-down-justice-league/ | work = Slash Film | date = 2008-04-10 | accessdate = 2008-11-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080920025807/http://www.slashfilm.com/2008/04/10/jason-reitman-turns-down-justice-league/ | archivedate = 2008-09-20 }}</ref>。2007年9月，[[喬治·米勒|喬治·米勒]]簽約擔任導演<ref name="Diane Garrett"/>，{{link-en|巴利·奧斯朋|Barrie M. Osborne}}同時也將擔任監製<ref name=Osbourne/>，電影預計會有2.2億美元的預算<ref name=Canada/>。

在隨後的一個月，約四十名演員參與了試鏡，其中包括了[[約瑟夫·克羅斯|約瑟夫·克羅斯]]、[[邁克·安格拉諾|邁克·安格拉諾]]、[[馬克斯·泰瑞奥|馬克斯·泰瑞奥]]、[[敏卡·凱利|敏卡·凱利]]、[[安卓恩·帕利奇|安卓恩·帕利奇]]和[[斯科特·波特|斯科特·波特]]。米勒打算想要在電影的過程中讓人有「成長」的感覺，因此會想挑選年輕的演員來演<ref name=Kit>{{cite news | author = Borys Kit | title = The Vine: Young actors seek ''Justice'' | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date = 2007-10-15 | accessdate = 2008-03-16}}</ref>。[[D·J·科特羅納|D·J·科特羅納]]被選為飾演超人<ref name=NYT>{{cite news | author = Michael Cieply | title = A Film’s Superheroes Face Threat of Strike | work = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date = 2008-03-01 | accessdate = 2008-03-15}}</ref>，[[艾米·漢默|艾米·漢默]]將飾演蝙蝠俠<ref>{{cite news | author = Marc Malkin | work = [[E!|E!]] Online | url = http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/marc_malkin/b30975_holy_double_take_batman_here_comes_new.html | title = Holy Double Take, Batman! Here Comes a New Caped Crusader | date = 2008-09-25 | accessdate = 2008-11-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081104103251/http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/marc_malkin/b30975_holy_double_take_batman_here_comes_new.html | archivedate = 2008-11-04 }}</ref>。[[潔西卡·貝兒|潔西卡·貝兒]]在會談的過程中，拒絕了神力女超人一角<ref>{{cite news | author = Tatiana Siegel | title = Jessica Biel in talks for ''Justice'' | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117972674 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2007-09-24 | accessdate = 2008-03-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101104123220/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117972674 | archivedate = 2010-11-04 }}</ref>。之後改鎖定[[泰瑞莎·帕瑪|泰瑞莎·帕瑪]]和{{link-en|夏儂·索莎蒙|Shannyn Sossamon}}，而[[瑪麗·伊莉莎白·文斯蒂德|瑪麗·伊莉莎白·文斯蒂德]]也證實自己也曾試鏡過<ref>{{cite news | author = Shawn Adler | title = Mary Elizabeth Winstead Envisions Bulking Up For Wonder Woman | url = http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/10/26/mary-elizabeth-winstead-envisions-bulking-up-for-wonder-woman/ | work = [[MTV|MTV]] Movies Blog | date = 2007-10-26 | accessdate = 2008-03-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080325130525/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/10/26/mary-elizabeth-winstead-envisions-bulking-up-for-wonder-woman/ | archivedate = 2008-03-25 }}</ref>。最後由{{link-en|梅根·蓋爾|Megan Gale}}被選為神力女超人<ref name=youngcast>{{cite news | author = Diane Garrett; Michael Fleming | url = http://www.variety.com/VR1117979189 | title = Warner pulls plug on ''Justice League'' | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2008-01-16 | accessdate = 2008-03-15}}</ref>，而帕瑪則被改選為[[塔莉亞·奧·古|塔莉亞·奧·古]]的演員<ref>{{cite news|author =Jami Philbrick|title=Exclusive: Teresa Palmer Still Wants to Play Talia Al Ghul in 'The Dark Knight Rises'|publisher=Movieweb.com|date=2010-11-20|accessdate=2014-09-06}}</ref>。在《Justice League: Mortal》的劇本中也有[[約翰·史都華_(DC漫畫)|約翰·史都華]]的出現，這原本由{{link-en|哥倫布·索特|Columbus Short}}飾演<ref>{{cite news | author = Larry Carroll | title = Columbus Short Turns Down Lantern Ring For ''Justice League'' | work = [[MTV|MTV]] Movies Blog | date = 2007-10-30 | url = http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/10/30/columbus-short-turns-down-lantern-ring-for-justice-league/ | accessdate = 2008-03-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080311201231/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/10/30/columbus-short-turns-down-lantern-ring-for-justice-league/ | archivedate = 2008-03-11 }}</ref>，但後來改為嘻哈歌手[[凡夫俗子_(歌手)|凡夫俗子]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Shawn Adler | title = Common Confirms He’s Green Lantern In ''Justice League'' | work = [[MTV|MTV]] Movies Blog | date = 2008-02-08 | url = http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/02/08/exclusive-common-confirms-hes-green-lantern-in-justice-league/ | accessdate = 2008-03-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080315093307/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/02/08/exclusive-common-confirms-hes-green-lantern-in-justice-league/ | archivedate = 2008-03-15 }}</ref>，[[亞當·布羅迪|亞當·布羅迪]]將飾演[[貝瑞·艾倫|貝瑞·艾倫／閃電俠]]<ref>{{cite news|author=Larry Carroll|url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/09/02/adam-brody-remembers-his-justice-league-flash-suit-before-the-project-sprinted-away-forever/|title=Adam Brody Remembers His 'Justice League' Flash Suit, Before The Project Sprinted Away Forever|publisher=MTV Splash Page|date=2009-09-02|accessdate=2014-09-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022000948/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/09/02/adam-brody-remembers-his-justice-league-flash-suit-before-the-project-sprinted-away-forever/|archivedate=2014-10-22}}</ref>，以及[[傑·巴魯契|傑·巴魯契]]被選作{{link-en|麥克斯韋·洛德|Maxwell Lord}}的演員<ref>{{cite news | author = Mike Sampson | url = http://www.joblo.com/jay-talks-jla-and-seth | title = Jay Talks 'JLA' and Seth | work = {{link-en|JoBlo.com|JoBlo.com}} | date = 2008-08-04 | accessdate = 2008-11-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080910180433/http://joblo.com/jay-talks-jla-and-seth | archivedate = 2008-09-10 }}</ref>。[[修·基斯-拜倫|修·基斯-拜倫]]據傳飾演[[火星獵人|火星獵人]]。[[水行俠|水行俠]]演員仍未定<ref name=Kit/><ref name=Canada/>。{{link-en|瑪麗特·艾倫|Marit Allen}}在2007年11月過世前曾被聘請擔任服裝設計師<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117976802 | title = Costumer Marit Allen dies at 66 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2007-11-30 | accessdate = 2008-03-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110128192437/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117976802 | archivedate = 2011-01-28 }}</ref>，且[[维塔工作室|维塔工作室]]也將參與製作<ref>{{cite news | author = Tom Cardy | title = Weta triumphs in clash of the superheroes | work = {{link-en|惠靈頓自治領報|The Dominion Post (Wellington)|The Dominion Post}} | date = 2008-01-07 | accessdate = 2008-03-15}}</ref>。

但因編劇罷工活動在同月開始，使得華納兄弟不得不擱置製作<ref>{{cite news | author = Michaela Boland | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117979263 | title = Australia denies killing ''Justice League'' | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2008-01-17 | accessdate = 2008-03-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110128105627/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117979263 | archivedate = 2011-01-28 }}</ref>；2008年2月，罷工活動結束後，華納兄弟和米勒希望立即開始拍攝<ref>{{cite news | author = Andrew Hornery | title = Gale is lassoed for film | work = [[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] | date = 2008-02-09 | accessdate = 2008-02-27}}</ref>，但製作又推遲了三個月<ref name=NYT/>。最初，電影將在[[悉尼|悉尼]]的{{link-en|澳大利亞福克斯製片廠|Fox Studios Australia}}拍攝<ref name=Canada/>，其他取景地包括在當地附近的大學<ref name=Osbourne>{{cite news | title = Sydney mooted as location for Megan Gale's ''Wonder Woman'' flick | work = [[每日電訊報_(澳洲)|The Daily Telegraph]] | date = 2008-02-20 | accessdate = 2008-02-27}}</ref>與作為{{link-en|快樂港|Happy Harbor}}的{{link-en|悉尼海港|Sydney Heads}}<ref name=tax/>。但{{link-en|澳大利亞電影委員會|Australian Film Commission}}否決了華納兄弟40%的退稅，因為儘管劇組大多是澳大利亞人，他們還是覺得華納兄弟沒有聘請足夠的澳大利亞演員<ref name=Canada>{{cite news | author = Garry Maddox | title = Unhappy feet may flee Sydney | work = [[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] | date = 2008-02-25 | accessdate = 2008-02-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Kyle Buchanan|url=http://www.vulture.com/2010/10/armie_hammer_interview.html|title=The Social Network’s Armie Hammer Talks Special Effects, Misogyny, and the Downside of Being Tall and Handsome|work=[[紐約_(雜誌)|New York]]|date=2010-10-20|accessdate=2014-09-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908133723/http://www.vulture.com/2010/10/armie_hammer_interview.html|archivedate=2014-09-08}}</ref>。米勒表示對於委員會丟掉了數億美元投資而感到相當沮喪<ref>{{cite news | author = Garry Maddox | title = Mega movie refused rebate | work = [[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] | date = 2008-03-19 | accessdate = 2008-03-19}}</ref>。後來只好改至加拿大的{{link-en|溫哥華電影製片廠|Vancouver Film Studios}}拍攝，但製作卻延遲至2008年7月，而華納兄弟仍相信能在2009年暑期推出電影<ref>{{cite news | author = Diane Garrett | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117981504 | title = Warner Bros. to serve 'Justice' in '09 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2008-02-26 | accessdate = 2008-03-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110129010136/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117981504 | archivedate = 2011-01-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming; Pamela McClintock | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117981560 | title = Film greenlights in limbo | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2008-02-27 | accessdate = 2008-03-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101108015026/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117981560 | archivedate = 2010-11-08 }}</ref>。

隨著製作持續延遲，且加上2008年7月的《[[黑暗騎士|黑暗騎士]]》的成功<ref>{{cite news|author=Casey Seijas|url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/03/09/exclusive-justice-league-movie-still-a-possibility-says-director-just-not-anytime-soon/|title=Justice League' Movie Still A Possibility, Says Director... Just Not Anytime Soon|publisher=MTV Splash Page|date=2009-03-09|accessdate=2014-09-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69ZvLhHBH?url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/03/09/exclusive-justice-league-movie-still-a-possibility-says-director-just-not-anytime-soon/|archivedate=2012-07-31}}</ref>，使華納兄弟決定把重心先放在英雄個人電影的發展上，讓導演[[克里斯多福·諾蘭|克里斯多福·諾蘭]]繼續完成《[[黑暗騎士：黎明昇起|黑暗騎士：黎明昇起]]》。2012年，DC娛樂公司高級副總裁格雷戈里表示：「我們正準備製作一部正義聯盟的電影，無論是現在還是從現在起的十年。但是，直到我們知道它是正確的，否則我們不打算拍出來，華納不會要做到這一點」<ref>{{cite news | author = Marc Graser; Dave McNary; David S. Cohen | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990659 | title = WB taps into ties at DC Comics | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2008-08-15 | accessdate = 2008-11-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022082544/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990659 | archivedate = 2012-10-22 }}</ref>。繼2011年的《[[綠光戰警_(電影)|綠光戰警]]》的失敗後，華納兄弟打算重啟該電影。同時，對於《閃電俠》和《神力女超人》的改編不斷擱置也打算重新再度發展。在《[[超人：鋼鐵英雄|超人：鋼鐵英雄]]》的拍攝完成不久後，華納兄弟聘請[[威爾·比爾|威爾·比爾]]為新的《正義聯盟》編劇<ref>{{cite news|author=Jeff Sneider|url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/beall-writing-justice-league-for-warner-bros-1118055082/|title=Beall writing ‘Justice League’ for Warner Bros.|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2012-06-05|accessdate=2014-09-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828100419/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/beall-writing-justice-league-for-warner-bros-1118055082/|archivedate=2014-08-28}}</ref>。華納兄弟公司總裁傑夫·羅賓諾夫解釋說，《[[超人：鋼鐵英雄|超人：鋼鐵英雄]]》定下了基礎讓電影邁入下一步<ref>{{cite web |last=Baldwin |first=Kristen |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/04/11/man-of-steel-dc-comics-superhero-movies/ |title='Man of Steel' will open door for more DC Comics superhero movies |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2013-04-11 |accessdate=2013-06-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131122223238/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/04/11/man-of-steel-dc-comics-superhero-movies/ |archivedate=2013-11-22 }}</ref>。電影將包含了其他[[DC宇宙|DC宇宙]]的角色<ref name="DCU">{{cite web |url=http://batman-news.com/2013/04/23/man-of-steel-director-zack-snyder-promises-references-to-dc-universe/ |title=‘Man of Steel’ director Zack Snyder promises references to DC Universe |work=Batman News |date=2013-04-23 |accessdate=2013-04-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130426002604/http://batman-news.com/2013/04/23/man-of-steel-director-zack-snyder-promises-references-to-dc-universe/ |archivedate=2013-04-26 }}</ref>和定下DC漫畫角色的共同虛構電影宇宙<ref>{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/superman-man-of-steel-shared-universe/ |title=‘Man of Steel’ Will Launch DC Shared Universe |last=Dyce |first=Andrew |publisher=ScreenRant |date=2013-04-11 |accessdate=2013-04-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130412052916/http://screenrant.com/superman-man-of-steel-shared-universe/ |archivedate=2013-04-12 }}</ref>。高耶表示，綠光戰警將會和2011年的版本沒有任何關係<ref>{{cite news|author=Brendon Connelly|url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/06/13/david-goyer-tells-me-how-man-of-steels-story-causes-the-justice-league-movie/|title=David Goyer Tells Me How Man Of Steel Will "Cause" The Justice League Movie|publisher=BleedingCool.com|date=2013-06-13|accessdate=2014-09-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140831103811/http://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/06/13/david-goyer-tells-me-how-man-of-steels-story-causes-the-justice-league-movie/|archivedate=2014-08-31}}</ref>。在《[[超人：鋼鐵英雄|超人：鋼鐵英雄]]》於2013年6月上映後，高耶被聘請撰寫續集，以及一部新的《正義聯盟》劇本，而貝歐的劇本則作廢<ref>{{cite news|author=Nikki Finke|url=http://deadline.com/2013/06/man-of-steel-sequel-underway-with-zack-snyder-and-david-s-goyer-517621/|title=‘Man Of Steel’ Sequel Underway With Zack Snyder And David S. Goyer|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2013-06-10|accessdate=2014-09-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140827113618/http://deadline.com/2013/06/man-of-steel-sequel-underway-with-zack-snyder-and-david-s-goyer-517621/|archivedate=2014-08-27}}</ref>。續集後來被改為《[[蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光|蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光]]》，除了[[亨利·卡維爾|亨利·卡維爾]]的超人外，還包括了[[班·艾佛列克|班·艾佛列克]]的蝙蝠俠和[[蓋兒·賈多特|蓋兒·賈多特]]的神力女超人，這讓《正義聯盟》的行程更加地顯著。此外，該宇宙與諾蘭的《黑暗騎士》三部曲並不共存，儘管諾蘭也有在《正義曙光》中擔任執行製片人<ref>{{cite news|author=Jon Lyus|url=http://www.heyuguys.com/david-goyer-justice-league-movie/|title=David Goyer talks about a Blank Slate and a New Batman for the Justice League Movie|publisher=HeyUGuys.com|date=2013-06-14|accessdate=2014-09-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908133150/http://www.heyuguys.com/david-goyer-justice-league-movie/|archivedate=2014-09-08}}</ref>。2014年4月，宣布[[查克·史奈德|查克·史奈德]]將根據高耶的劇本來執導《正義聯盟》<ref>{{cite news|author=Alex Stedman|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/zack-snyder-to-direct-justice-league-movie-1201165409/|title=Zack Snyder to Direct ‘Justice League’ Movie|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2014-04-27|accessdate=2014-09-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140914081429/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/zack-snyder-to-direct-justice-league-movie-1201165409/|archivedate=2014-09-14}}</ref>。據報導，華納兄弟請[[克里斯·泰瑞歐|克里斯·泰瑞歐]]在隔年7月改寫劇本<ref>{{cite news|author=Mike Fleming|url=http://deadline.com/2014/07/comic-con-batman-v-superman-chris-terrio-justice-league-809843/|title=‘Batman V Superman’ Scribe Chris Terrio For ‘Justice League’|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2014-07-25|accessdate=2014-09-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906175846/http://deadline.com/2014/07/comic-con-batman-v-superman-chris-terrio-justice-league-809843/|archivedate=2014-09-06}}</ref>。2014年10月15日，華納兄弟宣布電影將分拆成上下兩部，分別於2017年11月17日和2019年6月14日上映，導演皆為史奈德<ref name="releasedates"/>。2015年7月上旬，據透露，上集的劇本已由泰瑞歐撰寫完成<ref>{{cite news|title=Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice Scenes Described, Justice League Script Complete|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/456329-batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice-scenes-described-justice-league-script-complete#/slide/1|accessdate=2015-07-04|work=comingsoon.net|date=2015-07-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706000559/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/456329-batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice-scenes-described-justice-league-script-complete#/slide/1|archivedate=2015-07-06}}</ref>。查克·史奈德表示，本片受[[傑克·柯比|傑克·柯比]]的《{{link-en|新神|New Gods}}》啟發<ref>{{cite news|title=‘Justice League’ Villains and Mother Boxes Teased by Zack Snyder|url=http://collider.com/justice-league-movie-villains-mother-boxes/|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008142458/http://collider.com/justice-league-movie-villains-mother-boxes/|archivedate=2016-10-08}}</ref>。監製黛博拉·史奈德和查爾斯·羅文於2016年6月17日證實，第二部《正義聯盟》電影將會是一部獨立的故事<ref>{{cite news|title=JUSTICE LEAGUE WILL NOT BE A TWO-PART MOVIE AFTER ALL|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/06/21/justice-league-will-not-be-a-two-part-movie-after-all|accessdate=2016-06-22|work=ign.com|date=2015-06-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622125230/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/06/21/justice-league-will-not-be-a-two-part-movie-after-all|archivedate=2016-06-22}}</ref>。

