===拍攝===
2015年7月，據透露，正式拍攝將於2016年春季開始，在此之前會先執行《[[神力女超人_(2017年電影)|神力女超人]]》的拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last1=Jayson|first1=Jay|title=Dates Wonder Woman & Justice League Start Filming Confirmed|url=http://comicbook.com/2015/07/30/dates-wonder-woman-justice-league-start-filming-confirmed/|accessdate=2015-08-01|work=comicbook.com|date=2015-07-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801182416/http://comicbook.com/2015/07/30/dates-wonder-woman-justice-league-start-filming-confirmed|archivedate=2015-08-01}}</ref>。正式拍攝於2016年4月11日在英國東南部的[[華納兄弟利維斯登製片廠|華納兄弟利維斯登製片廠]]進行，其他拍攝地包括[[倫敦|倫敦]]、[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]和[[冰島|冰島]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Breznican|first1=Anthony|title=Justice League begins shooting April 11 - EXCLUSIVE|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/02/21/justice-league-starts-April-11?xid=entertainment-weekly_socialflow_twitter|accessdate=2016-02-22|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2016-02-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222235303/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/02/21/justice-league-starts-April-11?xid=entertainment-weekly_socialflow_twitter|archivedate=2016-02-22}}</ref><ref name="Apr2016BN" />。與[[查克·史奈德|查克·史奈德]]長期合作的攝影師{{link-en|方賴瑞|Larry Fong}}因行程上的衝突而沒法參與本片，所以改由{{link-en|法比安·華格納|Fabian Wagner}}擔任攝影師<ref name="Apr2016BN">{{cite news|last1=Begley|first1=Chris|title=Fabian Wagner is the cinematographer for ‘Justice League’|url=http://batman-news.com/2016/04/11/justice-league-cinematographer-fabian-wagner/|accessdate=2016-04-12|work=Batman News|date=2016-04-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411112542/http://batman-news.com/2016/04/11/justice-league-cinematographer-fabian-wagner/|archivedate=2016-04-11}}</ref>。[[班·艾佛列克|班·艾佛列克]]也被透露擔任本片的執行製片人<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/ben-affleck-elevated-justice-league-891514 | title=Ben Affleck Elevated to 'Justice League' Executive Producer | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2016-05-06 | accessdate=2016-05-24 | author=Borys Kit | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604132110/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/ben-affleck-elevated-justice-league-891514 | archivedate=2016-06-04 }}</ref>。2016年5月，據透露，[[傑夫·強斯|傑夫·強斯]]和強·柏格將參與電影的製作，而他們也會繼續參與《[[蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光|蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光]]》後的DC擴展宇宙電影<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/batman-v-superman-fallout-warner-895174|title='Batman v. Superman' Fallout: Warner Bros. Shakes Up Executive Roles (Exclusive)|website=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2016-05-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hayEWp8n?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/batman-v-superman-fallout-warner-895174|archivedate=2016-05-18}}</ref>。同月，[[傑瑞米·艾恩斯|傑瑞米·艾恩斯]]表示，《正義聯盟》的故事會比《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》更加地直線和簡單<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/event/article-3611038/Batman-v-Superman-Dawn-Justice-star-Jeremy-Irons-new-life-semi-retired-actor.html | title=Batman v Superman: Dawn Of Justice star Jeremy Irons on his new life as a semi-retired actor | Daily Mail Online | work=Daily Mail | accessdate=2016-06-12 | last=Moreton | first=Cole | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611204424/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/event/article-3611038/Batman-v-Superman-Dawn-Justice-star-Jeremy-Irons-new-life-semi-retired-actor.html | archivedate=2016-06-11 }}</ref>。強斯後來表示，本片將會比之前的DCEU電影更「充滿希望和樂觀」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/warner-bros-s-new-strategy-on-dc-lighten-up-superheroes-1473350000|title=Warner Bros.’s New Strategy on DC: Lighten Up, Superheroes|first=Ben|last=Fritz|date=2016-09-08|publisher=|accessdate=2016-09-12|via=Wall Street Journal|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911234538/http://www.wsj.com/articles/warner-bros-s-new-strategy-on-dc-lighten-up-superheroes-1473350000|archivedate=2016-09-11}}</ref>。摩莫亞在Instagram上透露，在倫敦的拍攝已截至2016年10月1日，接下來會於10月和整個11月在冰島進行<ref name="JLwrap">{{cite web | url=http://www.thewrap.com/jason-momoa-thanks-justice-league-crew-with-shirtless-photo-as-filming-wraps-photo/ | title=Jason Momoa Thanks ‘Justice League’ Crew With Shirtless Photo as Filming Wraps (Photo) | publisher=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] | date=2016-10-01 | accessdate=2016-10-02 | author=Joe Otterson | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002062855/http://www.thewrap.com/jason-momoa-thanks-justice-league-crew-with-shirtless-photo-as-filming-wraps-photo/ | archivedate=2016-10-02 }}</ref>。

===後期製作===
2017年5月22日，史奈德不得已退出電影的後製階段，以便妥善處理最近逝世的女兒，使得改讓[[喬斯·溫登|喬斯·溫登]]代替他的職務，並撰寫和執導史奈德原本要進行的額外補拍<ref name=":2" />。2017年7月，宣布本片在倫敦和洛杉磯經歷了長達兩個月的補拍，華納兄弟公司向劇組提供了約2500萬美元的預算（這比一般補拍的600萬美元至1000萬美元還高）<ref name=reshoots>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/news/justice-league-reshoots-1202502433/|title=‘Justice League’ Extensive Reshoots Causing Headaches for Star Schedules|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2017-07-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170724191051/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/justice-league-reshoots-1202502433/|archivedate=2017-07-24}}</ref>。由於卡維爾在參與補拍的同時也正拍攝《[[不可能的任務6|不可能的任務6]]》，其饰演的角色必須留著鬍子，也讓華納兄弟不得不使用特效來將卡維爾的鬍子去除掉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.in/How-much-work-it-will-take-to-digitally-remove-Henry-Cavills-mustache-for-Justice-League-according-to-visual-effects-artists/articleshow/59811141.cms|title=How much work it will take to digitally remove Henry Cavill's mustache for 'Justice League,' according to visual effects artists|publisher=Business Insider|date=2017-07-28|accessdate=2017-07-31|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731200743/http://www.businessinsider.in/How-much-work-it-will-take-to-digitally-remove-Henry-Cavills-mustache-for-Justice-League-according-to-visual-effects-artists/articleshow/59811141.cms|archivedate=2017-07-31}}</ref>。華納兄弟後來宣布，溫登獲得了共同編劇的掛名，以表揚他的協助和貢獻<ref name="Joss Whedon writing credit" />。

