==發行==
《正義聯盟》排於2017年在11月17日在美國上映<ref name="releasedates">{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/dc-movie-slate-revealed/|title=DC Comics Movies Announced: ‘Suicide Squad,’ ‘Wonder Woman,’ ‘Justice League,’ ‘The Flash,’ ‘Aquaman’|last=Fischer|first=Russ|publisher={{link-en|/Film|/Film}}|date=2014-10-15|accessdate=2014-10-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6TQ91KdDF?url=http://www.slashfilm.com/dc-movie-slate-revealed/|archivedate=2014-10-18}}</ref>。2016年6月4日，傑夫·強斯證實電影的正式片名為《正義聯盟》<ref>{{cite web | url=https://twitter.com/geoffjohns/status/738924011195793413 | title=Clearing up any misconceptions -- the Justice League movie is called "Justice League". | publisher=Twitter | date=2016-06-04 | accessdate=2016-06-04 | author=Geoff Johns | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609074423/https://twitter.com/geoffjohns/status/738924011195793413 | archivedate=2016-06-09 }}</ref>。而電影也含有[[IMAX|IMAX]]版本<ref>{{cite news|title=IMAX and Warner Bros. Extend Deal to Include 12 More Films|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/777749-imax-and-warner-bros-extend-deal-to-include-12-more-films#/slide/1|accessdate=2016-10-22|work=ComingSoon.net|date=2016-10-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022140910/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/777749-imax-and-warner-bros-extend-deal-to-include-12-more-films#/slide/1|archivedate=2016-10-22}}</ref>。該片最先於2017年10月26日在[[北京|北京]]舉行了全球首映<ref>{{cite web|last1=McDonagh|first1=Ross|title=A league of their own! Ben Affleck and Gal Gadot scrub up with their co-stars at the Beijing premiere of Justice League|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-5023069/Ben-Affleck-Gal-Gadot-premiere-Justice-League.html|website=Daily Mail|accessdate=2017-11-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108063103/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-5023069/Ben-Affleck-Gal-Gadot-premiere-Justice-League.html|archivedate=2017-11-08}}</ref>。

