==迴響==
===評價===
《正义联盟》获得好壞參半的評價，演员表现（尤其是加朵和伊薩米勒）获得称赞，但剧情被批不充实，特效画面差，反派太弱。影片基调碰到了两极分化的评价，部分人赞扬影片风格较之前的作品明快幽默，其他则认为不协调<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbr.com/justice-league-movie-review-roundup/|title=Justice League: What Critics Are Saying|author=Kevin Melrose|publisher=Comic Book Resources|date=2017-11-15|accessdate=2017-11-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115201226/https://www.cbr.com/justice-league-movie-review-roundup/|archivedate=2017-11-15}}</ref>。评论聚合网站[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根據379條評論只有40%的新鮮度，平均得分5.25／10，网站共识写道：“《正义联盟》超越了众多DC电影，但仅此一跃难以撼动继续拖累系列的浑沌的美学、羸弱的角色和混乱的打戏。”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/justice_league_2017 |title=Justice League (2017) |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2017-11-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171119062533/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/justice_league_2017 |archivedate=2017-11-19 }}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得了45分，评论52条<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/justice-league |title=Justice League reviews |publisher=[[CBS|CBS]] |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-11-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117133710/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/justice-league |archivedate=2017-11-17 }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落於「B+」<ref name=opening/>。

《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的{{le|理查德·罗帕|Richard Roeper}}给予影片3.5星（满分4星），称赞了演员，尤其是加朵，表示“这是一部团结一心起源的电影，展现出极大的幽默和正能量”<ref>{{cite news |last=Roeper |first=Richard |date=2017-11-15 |title=Fun ‘Justice League’ cleverly assembles a superhuman fight club |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/fun-justice-league-cleverly-assembles-a-superhuman-fight-club/ |website=Chicago Sun Times |accessdate=2017-11-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115170811/https://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/fun-justice-league-cleverly-assembles-a-superhuman-fight-club/ |archivedate=2017-11-15 }}</ref>。《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的{{le|欧文·格雷伯曼|Owen Gleiberman}}对影片赞不绝口，他写道：“《正义联盟》的每一帧帧都在想着如何去弥补《蝙蝠侠大战超人》的罪过。这不仅只是一部续集——是为系列赎罪的之举。电影嘛，并不凌亂，不言过其实，很明快，很纯净，很淳朴（有时几乎太淳朴了），锋利的巧妙回答和激烈战斗并没有持续太久<ref>{{cite news|last1=Gleiberman|first1=Owen|title=Film Review: 'Justice League'|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/reviews/justice-league-review-ben-affleck-gal-gadot-1202614266/|accessdate=2017-11-15|work=Variety|date=2017-11-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115144700/http://variety.com/2017/film/reviews/justice-league-review-ben-affleck-gal-gadot-1202614266/|archivedate=2017-11-15}}</ref>。”

《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》的[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]给予影片2.5星（满分4星），称赞演员，但批评动作场面和编剧，他写道：“联盟成员聚集在一起的镜头都是在拌拌嘴，给影片掺入幽默和名副其实的感觉，给观众带来实在的兴趣。没有它，影片会是一盘散沙<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Travers|first=Peter|title='Justice League' Review: DC Superhero Team-Up Keeps It Light, For Better or Worse|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/peter-travers-justice-league-keeps-it-light-for-better-or-worse-w511641|work=Rolling Stone|date=2017-11-15|accessdate=2017-11-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115192311/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/peter-travers-justice-league-keeps-it-light-for-better-or-worse-w511641|archivedate=2017-11-15}}</ref>。”

相反，《[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]》的[[陶德·麥卡錫|陶德·麥卡錫]]在称赞加朵和米勒的同时，表示影片的画面丑陋且無趣，表示：“疲倦、重复和费劲的展现方式是这部作品的关键，还有值得注意的是，本·阿弗莱克第二次穿上蝙蝠装的模样，看上去他宁愿去别的地方，而不是这儿<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/justice-league-review-1057114 |title='Justice League:' Film Review |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2017-11-14 |accessdate=2017-11-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115135339/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/justice-league-review-1057114 |archivedate=2017-11-15 }}</ref>。”《{{le|Uproxx|Uproxx}}》的迈克·莱恩（{{lang|en|Mike Ryan}}）的想法类似：“也许日后这会是一个开起来很有意思的团队？伊萨·米勒的样子无疑是乐在其中，所以这很有前途。参演的演员都很优秀。他们只不过需要注意让演员们做点有趣的事情，咳咳，帕蒂·詹金斯，咳咳<ref>{{cite web|last=Ryan|first=Mike|url=http://uproxx.com/movies/justice-league-review/|title=‘Justice League’ Is A Drag And A Big Step Backwards For DC Movies|website=Uproxx|date=2017-11-15|accessdate=2017-11-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116003051/http://uproxx.com/movies/justice-league-review/|archivedate=2017-11-16}}</ref>。”

===票房===
在美國和加拿大，《[[富比士|富比士]]》早期預估《正義聯盟》能在首週獲得1.3億至1.7億美元的票房<ref>{{cite news|title='Justice League': The Optimistic Box Office Prediction|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/09/20/justice-league-the-optimistic-box-office-prediction/|accessdate=2017-10-03|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2017-09-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003231145/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/09/20/justice-league-the-optimistic-box-office-prediction/|archivedate=2017-10-03}}</ref>，而《{{link-en|BoxOffice (雜誌)|BoxOffice (magazine)|BoxOffice}}》則預估首週票房能達1.5億美元，且能在國內累積至3.3億美元<ref>{{cite news|title=Long Range Forecast: ‘Justice League,’ ‘The Star,’ & ‘Wonder’|url=http://pro.boxoffice.com/long-range-forecast-justice-league-the-star-wonder/|accessdate=2017-10-03|work={{link-en|BoxOffice (雜誌)|BoxOffice (magazine)|BoxOffice}}|date=2017-09-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923034303/http://pro.boxoffice.com/long-range-forecast-justice-league-the-star-wonder/|archivedate=2017-09-23}}</ref>。該片被分析在全球至少要達到6億至7.5億美元的票房才能收回成本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/news/justice-league-dc-reviews-box-office-ben-affleck-1202615975/|title=Can Warner Bros.’ Expensive, Long-Awaited ‘Justice League’ Deliver the Hit That DC Needs?|first=Ricardo|last=Lopez|publisher=Variety|date=2017-11-16|accessdate=2017-11-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116215330/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/justice-league-dc-reviews-box-office-ben-affleck-1202615975/|archivedate=2017-11-16}}</ref>。美國週四晚間，該片賺取了1300萬美元，高於6月的《[[神力女超人_(2017年電影)|神力女超人]]》（1100萬美元）<ref name=opening>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/justice-league-box-office-weekend-winner-wonder-the-star-1202210465/|title=‘Justice League’ Powers To $13M Thursday Night; Beats ‘Wonder Woman’ – Friday AM Update|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-11-17|accessdate=2017-11-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117080935/http://deadline.com/2017/11/justice-league-box-office-weekend-winner-wonder-the-star-1202210465/|archivedate=2017-11-17}}</ref>。該片在美國第一天（含週四的票房）獲得3880萬美元的票房，最終美國首週末票房僅收得9380萬美元，這對比《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》的1.66億美元降低了44%，同時這也是DCEU首部首週票房不到1億美元的電影。[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]認為，該片的首週成績會如此低歸因於《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》的不佳表現，以及直到前天才公布評分的[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]評級，這引起了觀眾的猜測和起疑<ref name=opening2>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/justice-league-opening-weekend-box-office-lower-thor-ragnarok-wonder-the-star-1202211094/|title=‘Justice League’ Encounters Kryptonite At The B.O. With $96M Opening: Why The DC Movie Weakened – Sunday AM Update|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-11-19|accessdate=2017-11-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171118210306/https://deadline.com/2017/11/justice-league-opening-weekend-box-office-lower-thor-ragnarok-wonder-the-star-1202211094/|archivedate=2017-11-18}}</ref>。

在國際市場上，《正義聯盟》在首週估計能開出2.15億至2.35億美元的票房，其中包括與美國同天上映的中國，分析師預估在首週全球票房能達至3.25億至5.5億美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/justice-league-wonder-woman-gal-gadot-global-box-office-opening-1202207757/|title=‘Justice League’ To Prevail Around The World With $325M+ Start – Box Office Preview|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2017-10-26|accessdate=2017-11-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115053853/http://deadline.com/2017/11/justice-league-wonder-woman-gal-gadot-global-box-office-opening-1202207757/|archivedate=2017-11-15}}</ref>。包括南韓、法國和巴西在內的九個國家於上映第一天便賺了850萬美元<ref name=opening/>。最終，該片從六十五個國家中在首週獲得了1.855億美元，其中包括了中國的5710萬美元、來自英國的980萬美元、來自墨西哥的960萬美元和來自南韓的880萬美元。在巴西，《正義聯盟》首週開出1420萬美元的票房，為該國史上最高的開盤數字<ref name=INTopening>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/justice-league-thor-ragnarok-coco-paddington-weekend-results-international-box-office-1202211796/|title=‘Justice League’ Lassos $185.5M Overseas, $281.5M WW; ‘Thor’ Rocks To $738M Global – International Box Office|first=Nancy|last=Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2017-11-19|accessdate=2017-11-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171119220704/http://deadline.com/2017/11/justice-league-thor-ragnarok-coco-paddington-weekend-results-international-box-office-1202211796/|archivedate=2017-11-19}}</ref>。

