==續集==
續集《正義聯盟2》定於2019年6月14日推出<ref name="releasedates"/>。儘管起初宣布《正義聯盟》將分成上下兩集，但後來查克·史奈德表示，兩部電影都是獨立的故事<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/snyder-calls-justice-league-complete-movie-says-sequel-still-track | title=Snyder Calls "Justice League" A "Complete Movie," Sequel Still On Track | publisher={{link-en|Comic Book Resources|Comic Book Resources}} | date=2016-06-23 | accessdate=2016-06-27 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160626043019/http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/snyder-calls-justice-league-complete-movie-says-sequel-still-track | archivedate=2016-06-26 }}</ref>。2017年3月，監製查爾斯·羅文宣布，史奈德將會回歸執導續集<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://comicbook.com/2017/03/06/man-of-steel-was-always-setting-up-the-future-dc-films-universe/ |title=Man of Steel Was Always Setting Up the Future DC Films Universe |date=2017-03-06 |website=Comicbook.com |access-date=2017-06-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170310034456/http://comicbook.com/2017/03/06/man-of-steel-was-always-setting-up-the-future-dc-films-universe/ |archivedate=2017-03-10 }}</ref>。2017年10月，J·K·西蒙斯表示，片商已開始進行續集的劇本製作<ref>{{cite web|last=Fitch|first=Adam|url=http://www.cbr.com/justice-league-2-written/|title=Justice League 2 Script Is Currently Being Written|date=2017-10-21|publisher=''CBR.com''|accessdate=2017-10-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022061508/http://www.cbr.com/justice-league-2-written/|archivedate=2017-10-22}}</ref>，但卻於2019年決定暫緩實施。

